&lt;/blockquote></description></item><item><title>哈工大(深圳)自动化专业 限选课选课说明及选课建议</title><link>https://hoa.moe/blog/selecting-distributive-lessons/</link><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hoa.moe/blog/selecting-distributive-lessons/</guid><description>
